    <abstract>
      <t>This document updates RFC 8029 and RFC 8611 that both define IANA registries for MPLS LSP Ping. It also updates the description of the procedures for the responses sent when an unknown or erroneous code point is found. The updates are to clarify and align this name space with recent developments.</t>
